message.content: Joe couldn't remember what they had been talking about or which "side" she would have to prop, only that significant any word slanted into her very soul a stem of warning, and with it was coupled a disembodied fragment of information, which now took on ominous significance: Nigel had been seen in Farlingham on an occasion he had sworn he had been standing in for Luke Parsons at his surgery in little Malopram.
